<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bertolt_Brecht&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: Secondary sources">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Secondary sources</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>[Anon.] 1952. "Brecht Directs". In <i>Directors on Directing: A Source Book to the Modern Theater</i>. Ed. Toby Cole and Helen Krich Chinoy. Rev. ed. Boston, MA: Allyn &amp; Bacon, 1963. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0023233001" class="internal">ISBN 0023233001</a>. 291- [Account of Brecht in rehearsal from anonymous colleague published in <i>Theaterarbeit</i>]</li>
